<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="present-n">present <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'preznt/    美 /'preznt/  </p>
<p>[常用the present]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>目前；现在：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ve decided to live in the present and not spend my life regretting the past or dreading the future.
我决定活在当下，不再浪费生命悔恨过去或担忧未来。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-present">at present</h3>
<p>1.<strong>现在；目前：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My classmate is at present in hospital with a broken leg. 
我的同学因为摔断了腿目前正在住院。</p><footer>2009 陕西改</footer></div>

<h3 id="for-the-present">for the present</h3>
<p>1.<strong>暂时 (for the moment)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We shall not need any more for the present. 
我们暂时不需要更多的了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I can’t remember it for the present. 
我一时想不起来了。</p></div></div>